{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_06_01_short",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 ドキドキ温泉旅行 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　遙子さん、今日はオフでしたよね？\nひょっとして、休みなのに何も予定がないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Haruko-san‚ you're off today‚ right?\nBy any chance‚ you don't have any plans for your day off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと何その言い方！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ what kind of way is that to say it!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "べ、別にやることがなくて暇を持て余したから\n事務所に顔を出した訳じゃないわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-It's not like I had nothing to do and\njust came to the office because I was bored!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "こう見えても私にはお友達が沢山いて\n休みの日はみんな私と遊びたいって引っ張りだこに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though it may not seem like it‚ I have lots of friends‚\nand on my days off‚ everyone wants to hang out with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ。自分で言ってて虚しくなってきちゃったわ\nええ、そうよ。本当は予定がなくて暇だったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…sigh. I feel empty even saying that.\nYes‚ that's right. I really didn't have any plans and was bored.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "オフに誰とも遊ぶ予定がなくたっていいでしょ！\n一人は寂しいから事務所に来たっていいでしょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay not to have plans with anyone on a day off‚ right?\nIt's okay to come to the office because I'm lonely and alone‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "誰も責めてませんよ。それに、遙子さんの\n予定が空いていてむしろ助かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No one is blaming you. Besides‚ Haruko-san‚\nit actually helps that you're free today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "助かったってどういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean by 'it helps'?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……\n今から俺と温泉旅館に行って一泊してもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san…\nCould you come with me to a hot spring inn for an overnight stay‚ starting now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}